schools.name: Martin Luther King Jr Elementary School

data.description:
Welcome to this stunning 3-bed, 3-bath home built in 2021 by Century Communities. This modern residence boasts a
spacious 2085 ft.² floor plan, complete with luxurious granite countertops, elegant luxury vinyl plank flooring, and a sleek
gas range in the kitchen. The home features a fully finished two-car attached garage with drywall, perfect for storage or
hobbies. Enjoy the large fenced backyard with a concrete patio, ideal for outdoor entertaining. Moreover, this home offers
the advantage of a VA assumable mortgage, making it an attractive option for eligible buyers. The property is 100%
landscaped and requires little to no maintenance. Enjoy all the benefits of a new build home without having to go through
the process! Don't miss the opportunity to own this contemporary gem and schedule your showing today!!! **Please note
that the square footage of this property, as recorded by the El Paso County Assessor's Office, is 2085 square feet. However,
according to the builder's website, the square footage is stated as 1605 square feet. Prospective buyers are advised to
conduct their own independent measurements and verifications to confirm the accurate square footage of the property to
their satisfaction prior to entering into any purchase agreement.**
